These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: swimming, cricket, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is swimming is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Sport   | volleyball | cricket | swimming |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
There 3 different types of food: pomegranate, lettuce, strawberry
1. the person eating lettuce is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating pomegranate is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Food   | pomegranate | strawberry | lettuce |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: traveling, gardening, reading
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3
3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Hobby   | traveling | gardening | reading |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: salsa, funk, folk
1. the fan of funk is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of funk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |  3   |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | folk | funk |

