.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-20::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, woodworking, magic-tricks
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is baking is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| Hobby   | woodworking | magic-tricks | baking |

 